# Architecture Standards

- Business logic lives **only in Services**
- Repositories access data only
- API views stay thin — never access models directly from views
- Reuse existing APIs; never duplicate endpoints or bypass services
- Vue components contain **no business logic** (use stores/composables)

## Election integrity (critical)

While an election is **OPEN**, never expose via REST, WebSocket, Vue UI, USSD, or SMS:

- Candidate rankings
- Vote totals
- Winners

## Performance

- Pagination for long lists; virtual scrolling for large datasets
- Redis caching where appropriate
- Lightweight WebSocket payloads

## Coding

Meaningful names, small focused methods, no dead code, no duplicated logic.
